{"tid":2348814,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"AOA酉奈 離開FNC…專屬合約終了","createTime":"2021-01-01T05:07:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T10:06:11.000Z","uid":74065,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5efccf66523cce67c40f362e035a1ebbb010ae13","tid":2348814,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T05:07:40.000Z","msg":"媒體名稱：日間SPORT<br />\n<br />\n新聞連結：<a href=\"http://naver.me/xZDvc8vE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnaver.me%2FxZDvc8vE&d=h8K6dYNnEA4rSgnLcindhTv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=a8480ac8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://naver.me/xZDvc8vE</a><br />\n<br />\n記者姓名：Hwang Jee Young<br />\n<br />\n新聞全文：<br />\n<br />\nAOA團體成員酉奈離開所屬經紀公司。<br />\n<br />\n1日FNC在官方公告上傳 &ldquo;與徐酉奈的專屬合約終了，在圓滿的商議後一起做出這個決定&quot;<br />\n，對8年間在FNC旗下活動的酉奈傳達了感謝之意。<br />\n<br />\n2012年以AOA成員出道的酉奈在隊內擔任主唱，於&ldquo;短裙&rdquo;、&ldquo;短裙&rdquo;等熱門歌曲中獲得<br />\n喜愛。在酉奈離開後，AOA成員剩下雪炫、惠晶、澯美三人。<br />\n<br />\n以下是FNC Entertainment 官方立場正文<br />\n<br />\n大家好，這裡是FNC Entertainment<br />\n<br />\n公司與所屬藝人徐酉奈的專屬合約到期不再續約。<br />\n雙方在圓滿的商議後一起做出這個決定。感謝過去8年作為本公司的歌手及演員積極活動<br />\n的徐酉奈。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n請各位為徐酉奈的新出發給與溫暖的支持及鼓勵。謝謝。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n欺凌團<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"357848d8e18e45aa27afa0015876af45e10b850b","tid":2348814,"uid":367769,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T05:18:29.000Z","msg":"得返三個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b830e4a259a193c07a43cd23721d9e830270aa11","tid":2348814,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"357848d8e18e45aa27afa0015876af45e10b850b","tid":2348814,"uid":367769,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T05:18:29.000Z","msg":"得返三個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/